    "TWO FASCIST ADMIT THEY ARE AFTER PLACE IN SUN Special to The Leader ROME Other governments may carry on an agressive policy of mili tary imperialism and yet explain that they are not militaristic or imperial istic hut the Fascisti government of Italy frankly admits that it is going after a place in the sun After the recent amalgamation of the nationalist blueshirts with tne Fascist blackshirts the united party of Fascism came out with an organ of official propaganda in the shape of the newspaper Impero which stands for the ideal of making Rome once again th mistress of the world Want Italian Empire The program of the united party of Fascism as set forth in the March 11 editorial of Impero speaks for Itself Says Impero Among the characteristic marks of the human soul we find the irresistible urge to war Also the sharp and ineradicable differnces between men born to com mand and men born to rule Well then these marks form the impregnable foundation of a new Im pero Italiano Seeing that fate has ordained that there shall be command Ing and obeying nations there is no nation more fit to command than tne Italian the"
